        "remove_vertical_spacing": false,
        "remove_horizontal_spacing": false,
        "liquid": "<div class=\"phyto-reviews-section\">\n\n  <div class=\"phyto-header\">\n    <h2>\n      Our Customers Say It Best — Real Results From The First Few Weeks\n    </h2>\n\n    <div class=\"phyto-rating\">\n      <span class=\"phyto-stars\">★★★★★</span>\n      <strong>4.8/5 Excellent</strong>\n      <span>1,750+ Reviews</span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"phyto-carousel\">\n\n    <div class=\"phyto-card\">\n      <img class=\"phyto-review-image\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1076/7378/0573/files/6745a9c2-eacb-416e-aa55-96c275012810.png?v=1782387806\" alt=\"Customer review\">\n      <div class=\"phyto-stars-card\">★★★★★</div>\n      <h3>The Fatigue I'd Normalized For Years Is Gone</h3>\n      <p>I’d spent years feeling like I was walking through fog, just 'normalizing' the exhaustion and the constant bloating. I thought it was just age or stress. I’d tried every supplement under the sun, but Phytoseed Labs is the first thing that actually cleared the clouds. It’s not just that the discomfort is gone. It’s that my energy is finally back. I feel lighter, clearer, and finally like me again. Or should I say, this is a new me, and that's what I wanted, a new me !!</p>\n      <div class=\"phyto-author\">Heather D.</div>\n      <div class=\"phyto-verified\">✓ Verified Purchase</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"phyto-card\">\n      <img class=\"phyto-review-image\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1076/7378/0573/files/ChatGPT_Image_Jun_19_2026_01_23_16_PM.png?v=1781869147\" alt=\"Customer review\">\n      <div class=\"phyto-stars-card\">★★★★★</div>\n      <h3>My Gut Feels Amazing Again</h3>\n      <p>I'd returned from travel with persistent gut issues. My naturopath pointed to a potential parasite load. Phytoseed Labs was her exact recommendation. Four weeks later my stool test came back clean and I feel incredible. I ordered a second pack for my wife after seeing my own results. Now we're both on it.</p>\n      <div class=\"phyto-author\">Simon R.</div>\n      <div class=\"phyto-verified\">✓ Verified Purchase</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"phyto-card\">\n      <img class=\"phyto-review-image\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1076/7378/0573/files/Screenshot_2026-06-19_at_1.05.16_PM.png?v=1781867661\" alt=\"Customer review\">\n      <div class=\"phyto-stars-card\">★★★★★</div>\n      <h3>More Energy Every Month</h3>\n      <p>My cycle has been more regular since I started. I was diagnosed with PCOS two years ago. My gynecologist recommended I work on inflammation and hormonal balance naturally. After 6 weeks of Phytoseed Labs, my clothes were already looser, 4 cm off my waist. I'm amazed. my cycle became noticeably more regular and my energy improved too !</p>\n      <div class=\"phyto-author\">Mary B.</div>\n      <div class=\"phyto-verified\">✓ Verified Purchase</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"phyto-card\">\n      <img class=\"phyto-review-image\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1076/7378/0573/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_qrwlaiqrwlaiqrwl.png?v=1781869943\" alt=\"Customer review\">\n      <div class=\"phyto-stars-card\">★★★★★</div>\n      <h3>My New Gut Health Routine</h3>\n      <p>I do a seasonal gut detox every year and Phytoseed Labs has replaced my old protocol entirely. The combination of oregano and black seed oil is just more complete. I feel lighter, cleaner, and my skin even cleared up.</p>\n      <div class=\"phyto-author\">Daniel M.</div>\n      <div class=\"phyto-verified\">✓ Verified Purchase</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"phyto-card\">\n      <img class=\"phyto-review-image\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1076/7378/0573/files/e8d14d2d-b000-4108-847f-643bd8866871.png?v=1782385624\" alt=\"Customer review\">\n      <div class=\"phyto-stars-card\">★★★★★</div>\n      <h3>The 'Unbuttoning My Pants' era is over</h3>\n      <p>I've had IBS for years and honestly didn't expect much. If you know the struggle of having to unbutton your jeans under the table at dinner because your bloating is so painful, you need this. I’d stopped wearing anything tight because I hated the shape of my belly when I was bloated. It felt like I was constantly 'hiding' behind loose clothes. I was skeptical about oregano oil, but Phytoseed Labs is the only thing that has actually flattened the bloat and let me wear what I want without fear. It’s a total game-changer for my confidence.</p>\n      <div class=\"phyto-author\">Camilla H.</div>\n      <div class=\"phyto-verified\">✓ Verified Purchase</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"phyto-card\">\n      <img class=\"phyto-review-image\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1076/7378/0573/files/86b371ea-76eb-473b-8aa4-a3ed39561d04.jpg?v=1782386464\" alt=\"Customer review\">\n      <div class=\"phyto-stars-card\">★★★★★</div>\n      <h3>I Ate Well But Still Felt Bloated</h3>\n      <p>I was eating healthily, but my stomach still felt bloated after nearly every meal. No matter what I tried, nothing seemed to change. Within a few days of taking Phytoseed Labs, I noticed a real difference. Now I can enjoy my meals and dairy without worrying about discomfort afterwards.</p>\n      <div class=\"phyto-author\">Stephanie M.</div>\n      <div class=\"phyto-verified\">✓ Verified Purchase</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"phyto-card\">\n      <div class=\"phyto-stars-card\">★★★★★</div>\n      <h3>I Almost Didn't Bother Trying This One</h3>\n      <p>No more embarrassing stomach noises at work and no more discomfort after meals. I feel calmer and more comfortable from the inside out. I'd been looking for something that actually worked for years, and I'm so pleased I found Phytoseed Labs.</p>\n      <div class=\"phyto-author\">Peneloppe T.</div>\n      <div class=\"phyto-verified\">✓ Verified Purchase</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"phyto-card\">\n      <div class=\"phyto-stars-card\">★★★★★</div>\n      <h3>Only One Month And I Can Already Tell The Difference</h3>\n      <p>Bloating used to control my entire life. Planning outfits around how 'big' my stomach would get, turning down social events because I felt too uncomfortable, constantly feeling sluggish and drained. My doctor had me on so many elimination diets, I felt like I was punishing myself, but the bloat always returned. I was desperate for a natural solution that didn't involve more restrictions. Phytoseed Labs Oregano Oil with Black Seed Oil has been a game-changer. It's subtle, but incredibly effective. I no longer dread meal times, and the constant heavy feeling is gone. I have more energy, my digestion feels smoother, and for the first time in ages, I feel truly comfortable in my own skin. It's allowed me to live my life again without that constant, nagging discomfort. Highly, highly recommend!</p>\n      <div class=\"phyto-author\">Sophie L.</div>\n      <div class=\"phyto-verified\">✓ Verified Purchase</div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<style>\n\n.phyto-reviews-section {\n  background: #F6F4E6;\n  padding: 70px 0;\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n\n.phyto-header {\n  max-width: 1400px;\n  margin: 0 auto 40px;\n  padding: 0 30px;\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 20px;\n  flex-wrap: wrap;\n}\n\n.phyto-header h2 {\n  font-size: 42px;\n  line-height: 1.2;\n  color: #2F3527;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  margin: 0;\n}\n\n.phyto-rating {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 15px;\n  flex-wrap: wrap;\n}\n\n.phyto-stars {\n  color: #00B67A;\n  font-size: 24px;\n  letter-spacing: 3px;\n}\n\n.phyto-rating strong {\n  font-size: 30px;\n  color: #2F3527;\n}\n\n.phyto-rating span:last-child {\n  font-size: 24px;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  color: #2F3527;\n}\n\n.phyto-carousel {\n  display: flex;\n  gap: 30px;\n  overflow-x: auto;\n  padding: 0 30px 20px;\n  scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;\n}\n\n.phyto-carousel::-webkit-scrollbar {\n  height: 6px;\n}\n\n.phyto-carousel::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {\n  background: #56683F;\n  borde